 &lt;BR&gt; 
6.	The figures for the last quarter of previous period are balancing figures between the audited figures for the period from January 1, 2020 to December 31, 2020 and the figures from January 1, 2020 to September 30, 2020. The figures up to the end of the third quarter of previous financial period has been subjected to limited review. &lt;BR&gt; 
